_sText:
Destroyed wall + sequence *NOW WITH GIBS!*

Made by The Giblets of Jesus

Same as the old wall, only now, you have lovely little gibs :D

I couldn't decide on which gibs to use, so I included some large and small ones for you to use, each in separate vis groups and names.

There are also 2 buttons included in the .vmf, the one with the orange back will use the large gibs, and the grey backed one with use the small gibs.

As with all my prefabs, if you do decide to use this prefab in one of your fine maps, I'd like to be credited for the prefab used :).
